{"title":"大漠之行——腾格里放歌（图片）","authors":["张仃灰娃"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":8,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大漠之行——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腾格里放歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张仃画灰娃诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起伏的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大漠腾格里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热浪翻滚游动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手挨着手密密层层"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜂拥着冲开气流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿若无边的森林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横空一齐指向西极"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这浩瀚的流程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奏鸣亮色哨音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像箭簇穿透我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心房封藏的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愧悔无论是得意还是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑黑越的委屈怨恨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耀眼的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大漠腾格里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白热的光之海在日午摇摆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇摆着铃铛紫铜色的清响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半夜里月光汹涌起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深红的玫瑰狂热绽开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个风库沙原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窃议一场哗变"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是岁月沧桑开始模糊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今生前世都被焚尽勾销"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不由人便向往葬身这"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远达天边的合声流韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}